<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="261" type="type_taxon">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1940,2038]" pageId="1" pageNumber="261">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,311,1940,1966]" pageId="1" pageNumber="261">
<typeStatus box="[151,210,1940,1966]" pageId="1" pageNumber="261">Type</typeStatus>
species:
</emphasis>
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Silvestri" baseAuthorityYear="1895" box="[320,618,1940,1966]" class="Diplopoda" family="Chelodesmidae" genus="Sandalodesmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polydesmida" pageId="1" pageNumber="261" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="salvadorii">
<emphasis box="[320,618,1940,1966]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="261">Sandalodesmus salvadorii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Silvestri, F." box="[635,835,1940,1967]" pageId="1" pageNumber="261" pagination="1 - 12" refId="ref6358" refString="Silvestri, F. (1895) Viaggio del dottor Alfredo Borelli nella Repubblica Argentina e nel Paraguay. XIV. Chilopodi e Diplopodi. Bollettino del musei di zoologia e di anatomia comparata della Reale Universita di Torino, 10 (203), 1 - 12. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 8048" type="journal article" year="1895">Silvestri, 1895: 4</bibRefCitation>
, fig. 3), designated herein in accordance with ICZN Art.67.2. and Art.69.1., since the particular status of 
<taxonomicName authority="Silvestri, 1902" authorityName="Silvestri" authorityYear="1902" box="[765,1061,1976,2002]" class="Diplopoda" family="Chelodesmidae" genus="Sandalodesmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polydesmida" pageId="1" pageNumber="261" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bertonii">
<emphasis box="[765,885,1976,2002]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="261">S. bertonii</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Silvestri, F." box="[895,1061,1976,2002]" pageId="1" pageNumber="261" pagination="1 - 25" refId="ref6421" refString="Silvestri, F. (1902) Viaggio del Dr. A. Borelli nel Matto Grosso. VII. Diplopodi. Bollettino del musei di zoologia e di anatomia comparata della Reale Universita di Torino, 17 (432), 1 - 25. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 26628" type="journal article" year="1902">Silvestri, 1902</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is complex (see 
<bibRefCitation author="Hoffman, R. L." pageId="1" pageNumber="261" pagination="247 - 259" refId="ref5695" refString="Hoffman, R. L. (1982) Chelodesmid studies. XVIII. A synopsis of the genus Sandalodesmus Silvestri, 1902, and proposal of the new tribe Sandalodesmini (Polydesmida: Chelodesmidae). Spixiana, 5 (3), 247 - 259. https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 28194567" type="journal article" year="1982">Hoffman 1982: 247</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="262" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1436,150,285]" pageId="2" pageNumber="262">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,324,150,176]" pageId="2" pageNumber="262">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
Males of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Silvestri" authorityYear="1902" box="[447,621,150,176]" class="Diplopoda" family="Chelodesmidae" genus="Sandalodesmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polydesmida" pageId="2" pageNumber="262" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[447,621,150,176]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="262">Sandalodesmus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differ from those of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schubart" authorityYear="1958" box="[873,1072,150,176]" class="Diplopoda" family="Chelodesmidae" genus="Oncoleptodesmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polydesmida" pageId="2" pageNumber="262" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[873,1072,150,176]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="262">Oncoleptodesmus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(the only other member of the tribe) by the presence of only two macroseatae on dorsal side of gonocoxae (
<emphasis box="[1016,1039,187,212]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="262">vs</emphasis>
. several ones in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schubart" authorityYear="1958" box="[1228,1427,186,212]" class="Diplopoda" family="Chelodesmidae" genus="Oncoleptodesmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polydesmida" pageId="2" pageNumber="262" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1228,1427,186,212]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="262">Oncoleptodesmus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) and absence (
<emphasis box="[303,326,223,248]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="262">vs</emphasis>
. presence) of spinulations associated with the lateral margin of the acropodite process (except in 
<taxonomicName authority="(Schubart, 1958))" authorityName="" baseAuthorityName="Schubart" baseAuthorityYear="1958" class="Diplopoda" family="Chelodesmidae" genus="Sandalodesmus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polydesmida" pageId="2" pageNumber="262" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="repandus">
<emphasis box="[1415,1429,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="262">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[151,254,258,284]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="262">repandus</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Schubart, O." box="[269,441,258,285]" pageId="2" pageNumber="262" pagination="23 - 32" refId="ref6273" refString="Schubart, O. (1958) &quot; Leptodesmidae &quot; Brasileiras. VI: Especies novas do Estado do Rio Grande do Sul (Diplopoda, Proterosper- mophora). Revista brasileira de biologia, 18 (1), 23 - 32." type="journal article" year="1958">Schubart, 1958</bibRefCitation>
))
</taxonomicName>
(modified from 
<bibRefCitation author="Hoffman, R. L." box="[645,812,258,284]" pageId="2" pageNumber="262" pagination="247 - 259" refId="ref5695" refString="Hoffman, R. L. (1982) Chelodesmid studies. XVIII. A synopsis of the genus Sandalodesmus Silvestri, 1902, and proposal of the new tribe Sandalodesmini (Polydesmida: Chelodesmidae). Spixiana, 5 (3), 247 - 259. https: // www. biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 28194567" type="journal article" year="1982">Hoffman 1982</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
